  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 213.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then to try to organize, again, the minimal hygiene or to, within a matter of days, to persuade women, young women particularly, to cut their hair, because there was an outbreak of lice right away, to try to provide enough water.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You have to understand, there was no hot and cold running water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And if there was an outhouse in the back of a, of, of this lumber yard, that-- there were maybe 1,000 people around.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And so you had to provide some other means.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was a-- an unbelievable undertaking, which was literally unorganized and unrecognized by the Jewish community authorities in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Eventually, when our turn came or a few days before that, the ghetto was established on Star Street about the, the side-- on both sides of the street where the ritual bath was or where the Jewish community center was.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I, I don't mean by center a center like here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "What I mean is the-- where the offices were of the council and where the [INAUDIBLE] lived and where the entrance was to the, to the yard within which the shul wa-- the [INAUDIBLE] was and where all of these functionaries lived.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And on both sides of Star Street, to a depth of about, I would say, a block or a block and a half until the next street, they squeezed the Jews into the homes of the Jews who had lived there in normal times.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And then it became somewhat more organized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the-- the Jewish leadership of Kisvarda, in effect, was transformed into the Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And then there was a, a Jewish so-called police established.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And there was some allotment of food-- very minimal-- so that immediately, we had to begin to organize some kind of a, an underground food supply.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
